label yuugen_house_intro:
    scene yuugen_entrance with bgwipe
    show ingram with dissolve
    "The both of you return home, weary from a long day."
    "On the way here, you learned that this place is called 'Yuugen House'."
    "Not only is it where Ingram lives, but also where other vagabonds temporarily stay."
    scene blank with bgwipe
    scene bedroom_evening with bgwipe
    show ingram with dissolve
    "Ingram shows you where your room is."
    "You find it has a comfy atmosphere, perfectly balanced between traditional & modern."
    "He tells you to rest well, since the next few days will be busy with cafe training."
    "You nod, wishing him goodnight as he leaves."
    hide ingram with dissolve
    emi "Alright, let's get some rest."
    scene bedroom_night with dissolve
    "As you tuck yourself in, you stare at the trees swaying outside."
    "You try to recollect everything you've learnt since earlier."
    "Nobaros, vagabonds, spirit guiding..."
    "You couldn't help but wonder why you were there."
    "Ingram had said that vagabonds are those who are caught between life and death."
    "So did that mean there was a chance you died?"
    "You shudder at the thought."
    emi "(Never mind. I don't want to think about that.)"
    emi "(Surely, I'm still alive... I just need to remember what happened to me.)"
    "A wave of drowsiness suddenly washes over you."
    "With the sound of leaves swaying in the wind, you drift off to dreamland."
    scene blank with fade
    "PROLOGUE COMPLETE"
    return